Paper: hep-th/9907076

Date: 1999-07-11

Title: Heat Kernel Expansion for Semitransparent Boundaries

Authors: M. Bordag, D.V. Vassilevich

Comments: 16 pages

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A32 (1999) 8247-8259

We study the heat kernel for an operator of Laplace type with a$\delta$-function potential concentrated on a closed surface. We derive thegeneral form of the small $t$ asymptotics and calculate explicitly severalfirst heat kernel coefficients.